Package it.polimi.ingsw.PSP48.server.model.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DivinityPowerException
    Exception thrown when a move isn't allowed due to another divinity power
    DomedCellException
    Exception thrown when an action is blocked because the destination cell contains a dome
    IncorrectLevelException
    Exception thrown when a move isn't allowed due to a wrong level
    MaximumLevelNotReachedException
    Exception thrown when some action is blocked because the destination cell isn't at the maximum level
    MaximumLevelReachedException
    Exception thrown when some action is blocked because the destination cell is at the maximum level
    NotAdjacentCellException
    Exception thrown when some action is blocked because the destination cell isn't adjacent to the worker cell
    NoTurnEndException
    Exception thrown when some action is blocked because the action will block the player from completing the turn
    OccupiedCellException
    Exception thrown when some action is blocked because the destination cell is occupied
